01:21:04.307 --> 01:21:06.643
You know how to get
to this Nafiz guy?

01:21:06.893 --> 01:21:08.311
Yes, sir.

01:21:08.937 --> 01:21:10.230
Listen to me, man.

01:21:11.440 --> 01:21:13.483
I know you wanna make a
difference in this war.

01:21:14.192 --> 01:21:15.902
So do I.

01:21:16.778 --> 01:21:18.989
See, the thing about
what you're doin',

01:21:19.239 --> 01:21:22.409
I'm your A-Slash, I'll
follow you anywhere, man.

01:21:22.534 --> 01:21:25.078
But you need to ask yourself
if you are ready to live

01:21:25.203 --> 01:21:28.248
