of your decision.

01:21:28.748 --> 01:21:30.684
We're marines.

01:21:30.709 --> 01:21:32.836
We're the tip of the spear.

01:21:34.504 --> 01:21:36.965
I'm not gonna
let that woman die.

01:21:41.761 --> 01:21:44.473
We go in at dawn
during morning prayer.

01:22:17.130 --> 01:22:19.341
Are you sure she's in there?

01:22:23.470 --> 01:22:25.405
We can't go in
through the front door.

01:22:25.430 --> 01:22:27.849
There is another way.
Follow me.

01:22:45.242 --> 01:22:47.427
Once we're inside,
where's she gonna be?

01:22:47.452 --> 01:22:49.679
FAISAL: In the Nafiz's
chambers or imprisoned.

01:22:49.704 --> 01:22:51.164
So we find her and then what?

01:22:51.623 --> 01:22:53.183
Then we fight.

01:22:53.208 --> 01:22:55.101
We're going in silent.

01:22:55.126 --> 01:22:58.213
That means no gunfire until
it's absolutely necessary.

