ANOOSH: Help!

01:30:05.098 --> 01:30:06.950
(SPEAKING IN LOCAL LANGUAGE)

01:30:06.975 --> 01:30:07.976
Here!

01:30:13.022 --> 01:30:14.023
(ANOOSH WHIMPERING)

01:30:18.778 --> 01:30:21.322
Let's get you
outta here. Let's go.

01:30:35.920 --> 01:30:37.338
Marines! Standard
diamond formation.

01:30:37.505 --> 01:30:38.982
Package in the middle.
Khalid, shield her.

01:30:39.007 --> 01:30:40.066
Yes, sir!

01:30:40.091 --> 01:30:41.192
MERRIMETTE: All right, move out.

01:30:41.217 --> 01:30:42.427
(SHOUTING IN LOCAL LANGUAGE)

01:31:11.914 --> 01:31:15.251
