I'll hold them off!

01:31:29.849 --> 01:31:31.142
Kettner, let's go!

01:31:34.145 --> 01:31:36.230
I'll make my stand here.

01:31:37.065 --> 01:31:38.399
Go!

01:31:45.740 --> 01:31:47.158
Looks like I'm stayin'!

01:31:47.909 --> 01:31:49.911
Come on, let's move!

01:32:00.880 --> 01:32:02.131
Chris, move or die.

01:32:02.340 --> 01:32:03.424
Chris!

01:32:04.884 --> 01:32:07.303
Don't you have
some paperwork to do?

01:32:17.313 --> 01:32:18.314
