want real Virginia Brunswick stew,

01:33:24.172 --> 01:33:26.007
you gotta use rabbit.

01:33:26.924 --> 01:33:28.509
I prefer lamb.

01:33:29.177 --> 01:33:31.053
Never tried it with lamb.

01:33:33.639 --> 01:33:35.474
Danni, I don't have a shot!

01:33:39.979 --> 01:33:41.164
I'm movin' in.

01:33:41.189 --> 01:33:43.499
When we get home,

01:33:43.524 --> 01:33:46.736
I'll have my grandma make a big
ol' pot of Brunswick stew.

01:33:47.403 --> 01:33:48.779
I'll tell her to use lamb.

01:33:50.239 --> 01:33:52.175
There's plenty to go around,

01:33:52.200 --> 01:33:54.802
and I know the old gal
would love to have you.

01:33:54.827 --> 01:33:56.996
I would like that very much.

