01:34:23.731 --> 01:34:25.333
Let's get some, my brother.

01:34:25.358 --> 01:34:26.484
Let's do it.

01:34:28.069 --> 01:34:29.445
Come on.

01:34:33.532 --> 01:34:34.533
Let's go.

01:35:16.575 --> 01:35:17.785
MERRIMETTE: <i>A story.</i>

01:35:18.828 --> 01:35:21.122
<i>A man has a lot of choices,</i>

01:35:21.330 --> 01:35:24.583
<i>and these choices made in life
are rarely perfect.</i>

01:35:24.959 --> 01:35:27.420
<i>So he decides to sign a contract</i>

01:35:27.795 --> 01:35:29.772
<i>because he wants to
make a difference.</i>

01:35:29.797 --> 01:35:33.592
<i>He wants to save this world,
make it a better place.</i>

01:35:34.844 --> 01:35:37.321
<i>The consequences are punishing,</i>

01:35:37.346 --> 01:35:38.931
<i>unforgiving,</i>

01:35:39.348 --> 01:35:42.310
<i>and he questions why
he ever signed that contract.</i>

01:35:43.477 --> 01:35:45.688
<i>So what's the fucking point?</i>

01:35:46.272 --> 01:35:49.191
<i>I guess the point is
responsibility of duty.</i>

01:35:49.650 --> 01:35:51.444
<i>Love of country.</i>

01:35:52.320 --> 01:35:53.779
<i>A way of life.</i>

01:35:55.323 --> 01:35:57.700
<i>Are we on
the right side of this?</i>

01:35:57.992 --> 01:36:00.494
<i>These aren't our
questions to ask.</i>

01:36:00.661 --> 01:36:03.914
<i>A marine fights for the person
standing next to him.</i>

01:36:04.040 --> 01:36:06.667
<i>He fights for the man
who can't stand anymore.</i>

01:36:07.293 --> 01:36:11.355
<i>He fights so that others can have the
opportunity to make a difference.</i>

01:36:11.380 --> 01:36:14.592
<i>That's how we make
the unforgiving forgivable.</i>

01:36:15.092 --> 01:36:20.681
<i>And if we're lucky, somewhere in all the
fighting and dying, we discover hope.</i>

01:36:21.182 --> 01:36:24.060
<i>And the marines who killed
and bled and died</i>

01:36:24.518 --> 01:36:26.354
<i>will always be jarheads.</i>

01:36:27.772 --> 01:36:29.749
<i>Their families will have to live
with the unbearable demands</i>

01:36:29.774 --> 01:36:31.567
<i>of their ultimate sacrifice.</i>

