MARINE 1: Unidentified
vehicle, 12 o'clock!

01:36:52.338 --> 01:36:53.547
MARINE 2: Get out
of the truck!

01:36:54.256 --> 01:36:56.050
Show me your hands!

01:36:56.759 --> 01:36:58.552
U.S. Marines.

01:36:59.178 --> 01:37:00.196
Marine.

01:37:00.221 --> 01:37:02.848
Hey, it's me, Merrimette.

01:37:14.360 --> 01:37:15.778
Unload.

01:37:20.908 --> 01:37:22.243
Come on.

01:38:01.824 --> 01:38:03.742
Welcome home, Marines.

01:38:04.285 --> 01:38:06.120
It's good to have you back.

01:38:06.370 --> 01:38:08.122
